Introduction

Narin is a South Korean singer, rapper, and dancer under The Black Label. She is a member of the girl group MEOVV.

On August 29, 2024, Narin was revealed as the fifth and last member of MEOVV. The group officially debuted on September 6, 2024, with their debut digital single "MEOW".
